    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it just feels so selfish to stay when i know i'm only making things harder for them. if i leave, they can have a fresh start without all my mistakes weighing them down. wouldn't it be more selfless to just step aside so they can actually thrive? it feels like the only way i can truly be \"good\" for them is to not be there at all.",
