      "content": "I can see why you'd think that, but stepping aside isn't the answer. Your kids need you to show them that they're loved, even when things are hard. Leaving wouldn't be selfless, it would just be abandoning them. They need your flaws and mistakes to learn from, to understand that everyone makes mistakes. By staying, you're giving them the chance to see that they can overcome even the toughest challenges.",
